.\" Man page for ocode models
.TH OCODE-MODELS 1 "June 2025" "ocode" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ocode-models \- List available models
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ocode models
[\fIoptions\fR] [\fIprovider\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
List available LLM models from various providers. Models can be filtered by
provider name.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
\fIprovider\fR
Filter models by provider (e.g., openai, anthropic, google).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-provider\fR \fI<provider>\fR
Filter models by provider.
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Show this help message and exit.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
List all models:
.B ocode models
.TP
List models from OpenAI:
.B ocode models openai
.TP
Filter by provider flag:
.B ocode models --provider anthropic
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ocode (1)